The,Xchangeonline,API,provides,developers,with,currency,conversion,functionality,and,currency,rounding,functionality,All,exchange,rates,are,kept,current,Developers,simply,call,the,API,specifying,the,function,conversion,or,rounding,amount,of,money,the,current,currency,the,desired,currency,value,and,the,API,key,giving,them,access,to,the,service,The,API,then,returns,the,value,of,the,money,in,the,currency,desired,It,also,supports,a,wide,variety,of,development,platforms,and,over,different,currencies